Global Polythene Disposable Glove Market Insights
Polythene Disposable Glove Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Polythene Disposable Glove Market Overview
The global polythene disposable glove market size was valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion in 2023 and is projected to grow at a steady CAGR of 5.6% from 2024 to 2030. The market expansion is primarily driven by rising demand in industries such as foodservice, healthcare, and cleaning, where hygiene standards are paramount. With the increasing awareness about personal protection and safety, disposable gloves are increasingly being adopted for medical and non-medical applications. This trend is expected to continue, further boosting the market growth over the forecast period.

